Packed layout record Word has value: u16.

To checked dynamic layout index start: i32, giving i32.
Let bytes be buffer of 4 u8 filled with 0.
bytes at 1 becomes 42.
bytes at 2 becomes 0.
Let word be read Word from bytes at start.
Give word.value as i32.

To main, giving i32.
Give checked dynamic layout index 1.
